*aview-1.3.0_rc1 (1 Feb 2002)

  08 Aug 2002; Mark Guertin <gerk@gentoo.org> aview-1.3.0_rc1.ebuild :
  Fixed broken ${S}, and added to this ChangeLog (no one else has even though
